data.text:
Mai Zetterling was a Swedish actress and film director who portrayed Helga Eveshim, an old enemy of the Grand High Witch in the 1990 film The Witches. Born in V채ster책s, Sweden to a working class family, she started her career as an actress at the age of 17 at Dramaten, the Swedish national theatre, appearing in war-era films.
